==English==
===Noun===
'''click''' (''Plural:'' [[clicks]])

# a sharp, but not particularly loud sound produced, for example, by the operation of a [[switch]], a [[lock]], or a [[latch]]
#(''phonetics'') an [[ingressive]] sound made by [[coarticulation|coarticulating]] a [[velar]] or [[uvular]] closure with another closure
#the act of pressing a button on a computer [[mouse]]

===Verb===

'''to click'''

# To press and release a computer mouse button or other switch etc.
# To cause or emit a click

